---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric'
});
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - tecloudz">
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo"><a href="/">tecloudz.</a></div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/posts">Posts</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="policy-container">
    <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="policy-content">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>tecloudz</strong>. By accessing this website, we assume you accept these terms and conditions. 
        Do not continue to use tecloudz if you do not agree to take all of the terms and conditions stated on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Other than the content you own, under these Terms, tecloudz and/or its licensors own all the intellectual property rights and 
        materials contained in this Website. You are granted limited license only for purposes of viewing the material contained on this Website.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Tech Disclaimer (Important)</h2>
      <p>
        The content provided on <strong>tecloudz</strong> is for educational and informational purposes only. While we strive to provide 
        accurate and up-to-date information regarding software, apps, and technology, we make no representations or warranties of any kind, 
        express or implied, about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or suitability of the information.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Any action you take upon the information you find on this website is strictly at your own risk.</strong> 
        tecloudz will not be liable for any losses and/or damages in connection with the use of our website, including but not limited 
        to data loss, device malfunction, or software errors resulting from following our tutorials.
      </p>

      <h2>4. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by or in any way affiliated with tecloudz. 
        Please note that we do not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any information on these external websites.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        tecloudz is permitted to revise these Terms at any time as it sees fit, and by using this Website you are expected to review 
        these Terms on a regular basis.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="minimal-footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 tecloudz</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Reuse the exact same styles as your Privacy Policy */
  .navbar { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .logo a { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-main); }
  nav a { margin-left: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline; }

  .policy-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-main); }
  .meta { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .policy-content { line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-main); }
  .policy-content h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-main); }
  .policy-content p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) { h1 { font-size: 2rem; } .navbar { padding-bottom: 2rem; } }
</style>